bodyEn:
1. Vehicle {VEHICLE_NO} (Tag {TAG_ID}) was charged Rs. {AMOUNT} twice within minutes on {TXN_DATE} (UTRs {TXN_ID}, {TXN_ID_2}) at plaza {PLAZA_NAME}. Reverse the duplicate deduction.

Attachments: Tag statement, plaza receipt, ANPR screenshot (if available).

Regards,
{USER_NAME}
Mobile: {MOBILE_NO}

bodyHi:
